  "title": "Prime Mover Driver",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p><strong>.</strong>Possess a valid class 4/5 Driving License and <br /> experienced with driving Prime Mover</p><p><strong>.</strong>Trucking of empty or Loaded containers</p><p><strong>.</strong>Trucking location include PSA port and client’s <br />  yard </p><p><strong>.</strong>Trucking of Prime Mover according to <br /> instruction in Jurong Port and PSA\n compliance with respective regulations</p><p><strong>.</strong>Follow delivery container schedule within <br /> Singapore and familiar with roads in Singapore</p><p><strong>.</strong> To perform regular pre-operational checks on<br />  vehicle and equipment before operation</p><p><strong>.</strong>Handle container delivery and collection, shift<br /> the container within warehouse and yard</p><p><strong>. </strong>Responsible for proper care and maintenance <br />  of vehicle and equipment</p><p><strong>.</strong>Rotation shift work and 6 days work per week</p><p><strong>.</strong> To perform any other ad-hoc duties assigned by <br />  controller</p><p><strong>.</strong>Positive attitude and hardworking</p><p><strong>.</strong> 1 year experience in driving truck / primer mover</p>",
